1. *Traje* mi dosta dugo da dođem na posao svaki dan. (It takes me a long time to get to work every day.)
2. Svi traju različito dugo da se naviknu na novu okolinu. (Everyone takes a different amount of time to get used to a new environment.)
3. Ona je *trajala* dugo da shvati situaciju. (It took her a long time to understand the situation.)
4. *Trajući* pet minuta, vožnja je bila veoma duga. (Taking five minutes, the ride was very long.)
5. On će *trajati* još neko vreme dok ne završi zadatak. (He will take some more time to finish the task.)